---

<Layout>
  <main>
    <section class="h-fit bg-(--primary) text-(--secondary) py-16 sm:px-16 px-8 flex flex-row items-center justify-between">
      <div class="xl:w-[600px] lg:w-[480px] space-y-8">
        <div class="xl:w-[540px] lg:w-[440px] space-y-8">
          <h1 class="lg:text-4xl lg:leading-11 sm:text-3xl text-2xl font-(--font-secondary)">
            <span class="font-bold">Fortune Lead Co.</span> <br>
            A leading consultancy and training firm passionate about enhancing workplace performance.
          </h1>
          <p>At Fortune Lead, we believe empowered people build stronger organizations.</p
        </div>
        <form action="" class="w-full flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-3 sm:space-x-4">
          <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your best email" class="bg-white text-black px-4 py-3 w-full">
          <button class="bg-(--secondary) text-white px-4 py-3 w-full sm:w-fit text-nowrap">Get Started</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-black sm:p-16 p-8 space-y-4 w-screen">
      <h2 class="text-2xl">Our Approach</h2>
      <div class="h-full flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-start w-full space-y-8">
        <p class="xl:text-4xl text-3xl w-full flex-1 lg:w-1/4">The Growth <br> Catalyst Formula</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 gap-y-12 w-full flex-2">
          <div class="xl:w-[400px] md:w-[310px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Listen First</h3>
            <p>Every organization is unique, so we take time to understand your needs and tailor solutions that truly fit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-[400px] md:w-[310px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Deliver What Matters</h3>
            <p>From real-world tools to fresh ideas, we focus on impact, not just ticking boxes.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-[400px] md:w-[310px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We Walk the Journey with You</h3>
            <p>Our team is skilled, passionate, flexible, and committed to seeing you succeed.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="xl:w-[400px] md:w-[310px]">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">We are committed to excellence</h3>
            <p>From planning to execution, we uphold high standards in everything we do</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="sm:p-16 p-8 space-y-8 w-screen">
      <h2 class="text-2xl">Our Services</h2>
      <div>
        <Accordion acc_id="1" active=true title="Leadership development">
          <div class="text-left md:w-3/4">
            <p class="">We empower individuals and teams through dynamic,
              results-driven programs that shape transformative leaders.
              Our focus areas include:
            </p>
            <ul class="px-8 list-disc">
              <li>Self-Leadership</li> 
              <li>Team Effectiveness</li>
              <li>Strategic Alignment</li>
              <li>Effective Execution</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Accordion>
        <Accordion acc_id="1" active=false title="Human Resource Consulting">
          <div class="text-left md:w-3/4">
            <p class=""> We cultivate a safety-first culture through expert training, policy support, and compliance guidance. </p>
