              <li>Effective Execution</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </Accordion>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="sm:p-16 p-8 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl">About us</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start justify-start md:space-x-8 space-y-6 md:space-y-0">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p>Fortune Lead Co. is a leading consultancy and training firm passionate about enhancing workplace performance.</p>
          <p>At Fortune Lead, we believe empowered people build stronger organizations.</p>
          <p>We partner with teams and leaders to foster better leadership, safer workplaces, and thriving cultures.</p>
          <p>Through practical, people-centred solutions in leadership, safety, and HR, we deliver impact that lasts.</p>
          <p>With passion, experience, and creativity, we don’t just deliver solutions —we transform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sm:w-[480px]">
          <h3 class="text-2xl">Vision</h3>
          <p>To be Kenya’s leading catalyst for people growth.</p>
          <br>
          <h3 class="text-2xl">Core values</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Excellence</li>
            <li>Integrity</li>
            <li>Innovation</li>
            <li>Safety and Assurance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-2xl">Mission</h3>
      <p>To drive organizational transformation through innovative tailored, and high-impact solutions that exceed expectations.</p>
    </section>
    <section class="sm:px-16 px-8 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl">Our Team</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row space-y-6 md:space-y-0 items-center md:items-start md:space-x-12 xl:justify-center xl:space-x-56 justify-between lg:space-x-24">
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6 sm:w-[500px]">
          <img src="/david.jpeg" alt="Photo" class="md:w-[400px] w-[280px] rounded-full border aspect-square">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">David Kariuki</h3>
          <p> Human Resource & Leadership Expert | Certified Executive Coach <br> With 20+ years of experience in financial services, technology, and education, David specializes in organization design, culture transformation, talent strategy, and executive coaching. He has worked with leading organizations across East Africa, delivering impactful HR and leadership solutions </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-6 sm:w-[500px]">
          <img src="/namu.jpeg" alt="Photo" class="md:w-[400px] w-[280px] rounded-full border aspect-square">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">Richard Namu</h3>
          <p>Occupational Safety & HR Specialist | Certified Fire & Emergency Instructor <br> Richard brings over a decade of expertise in health & safety training, audits, and emergency response. His work spans humanitarian agencies, corporates, schools, and media houses across Africa, supporting organizations to build resilient and safe workplaces.</p>
        </div>
